item.title: foraging starter kit
item.description: foraging starter kit # so you want to eat stuff outside? # by Matte Kirwin last edited 06 April 2023 (sept 2022) i’m on vacation right now so this doc is incomplete. but it should have the bare minimum to get you started! getting inspired and learning # Videos: # Black Forager on TikTok and instagram is a great starting point. she’s incredibly informative, inspiring, and funny Books, general foraging # Northeast Foraging, if you live in the northeast of the US this book is the perfect starter book.
